Class Address

java.lang.Object
Address
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class Address extends Object implements Serializable
The Address class represents a serializable object that models an address. It includes information about the street, town, and postcode of the address. Implements the Serializable interface to support object serialization.
